Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspense and deduction closes the gap between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a beautiful garden a mysterious case occurs
