Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the treat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gee... This is such a great garden that's true to your title
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as the president of the Kiyama Furniture Company
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a nice house you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen a garden with a waterfall like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This garden somehow makes me feel at peace
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You like my garden.\NI'm glad I brought you up here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You like my garden.\NI'm glad I brought you up here too.\NMichiyoshi Majima
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you like my garden.\NI'm glad I brought you up here too.\NMichiyoshi Majima\NDI DI all.Â»\NO v9 fr C Let)\NXLRI MR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you like my garden.\NI'm glad I brought you up here too.\NLe & &UL w PF fr CC LoTOoD\NKIRA T
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you like my garden.\NI'm glad I brought you up here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's about time to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? To begin what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Water is flowing over the basin of the waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Clio, Tl
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water is filling the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hahaha Surprised, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me explain how this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 8am... 4 p.m. and 8 p.m. three times a day, the water flows into the garden
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in doing so, won't the sand pattern disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Water is poured in slowly so that the pattern is not lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then the water is drained in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's quite highly reputed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The former president made this device.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you'll excuse me for a moment,\NI'd like to get back to work
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But make yourselves at home.\NSee you at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And don't worry about your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get my secretary to pick it up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank so much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'd have done the same for me if I were in your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK then. I'll leave them to you, Ayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well, President...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy oh boy, what ajtruly superb view!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heck! What carefree jokers they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't they realize how costly it is to maintain it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The garden Kiyama made is really nothing but a big nuisance for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, we can see clearly through the circles of white sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bet it's especially romantics at night when the moon is reflected on the water
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We even have guests who come here every full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wonderful to drink cold sake while viewing a full moon rising from behind Mt. Fuji
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phew!\NIt's out of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there. Something's by the pillar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that! It's a catching pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Catching pole?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, when someone drops something on the white sand of the yard,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we lengthen this pole and pick it up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't step on the wave pattern of the white sand, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. It's well thought out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since Mr. Majima became president, the - gardener comes only once a month. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty mind racking, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty mind racking, isn't it...
