Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He is a travelogue writer who travels to many countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've read your\NWandering Through Africa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you
