Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be holding a photo exhibition
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if it's okay with you, please come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Thank you, are you sure it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll sign my autograph now...
